		<span class="sys-font-heading3 sys-rhp-color-title">Administrator Options</span><br />
	        <br>
			<div class="8pt">

			<b>Update multiple operating systems<br /></b>
			To select from updates issued for all Windows operating systems, including software updates for servers and driver (hardware) updates, search the <a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=8973" target="_blank" class="sys-link-normal">Windows Update Catalog</a>.<br /><br />
			<b>Manage the update process for networks<br /></b>
			To update Windows operating systems and other Microsoft products running inside your corporate firewall, use <a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=24462" target="_blank" class="sys-link-normal">Windows Update Services</a>. This solution (previously known as Software Update Services (SUS) 2.0) helps administrators target systems for deployment, control user interactions, remove updates, schedule the frequency and priority of updates, and more.<br /><br />
			Note:<br />
			<ul style="margin-left:40px">
				<li>The <a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=27549" target="_blank" class="sys-link-normal">Microsoft Baseline Security Analyzer (MBSA)</a> also scans and reports common security-related misconfigurations and can help you install missing security updates for Windows-based computers. </li>
				<li>
					To quickly view which updates are delivered by Automatic Updates, Windows Update, and Windows Update Services, read the 
					<a  class="sys-link-normal" href="about.aspx?ln=en" target="eContent">Windows Update FAQs</a>
					.
				</li>
			</ul>
			<br/><b>Get more updates<br /></b>
			<ul style="margin-left:40px">
				<li><a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=21601" target="_blank" class="sys-link-normal">Search the Microsoft Download Center</a>
			<br>Get downloads for all supported Microsoft products. Downloads are available in 30 languages.  
		</li>
				<li><a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=24459" target="_blank" class="sys-link-normal">Visit Microsoft Office Online</a>
			<br>Find updates for the Microsoft Office system, versions 97/98 and later. Downloads include templates, assistance content, and clip art.
		</li>
				<li><a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=27098" target="_blank" class="sys-link-normal">Become a Microsoft Premier Support customer</a>
			<br>Learn about Premier Support benefits, including additional updates such as pre-release software.   
		</li>
			</ul>
			</div> 
